context_meta.summary: COUNTRYSIDE, Ill., Dec. 18, 2017 /PRNewswire-iReach/ -- Chicago drivers looking to get behind the wheel of a new SUV model in the coming months know that the segment is among the most competitive in the auto industry. To help simplify its customer's shopping processes, one Chicago-area dealership has taken it upon itself to post helpful model comparisons to its website. The reviews give readers a clear idea of how similar models fare against each other. In its comparison between the 2018 Mitsubishi Outlander and the 2018 Nissan Rogue, the Continental Mitsubishi highlighted different areas in which the models differ as well as aspects that were the same or similar between the two.

context_meta.title: X-Men, Fantastic Four will be home now: Lee on Disney-Fox deal
context_meta.summary: Popular comic book writer Stan Lee says in the wake of the historic Disney-21st Century Fox merger, characters from franchises such as "X-Men" and "Fantastic Four" can finally come back to Marvel, their home. The 94-year-old legend's comments come after Disney CEO Bob Iger announced that the MCU will incorporate these franchises, including "Deadpool", after their USD 52.4 billion-worth buyout plan for Fox is complete. Now characters such as the X-Men and the Fantastic Four can come home to the place where they belong.
